Description:
    This generator will create two files. One for setting up admin password and another setting up publish server

Example:
    rails generate rubber_ring:install

    This will create
        create app/config/publish.yml
        create app/config/initializers/rubber_ring.rb
        create app/views/layouts/rubber_ring/application.html.erb
        create app/assets/javascripts/application.js
        create public/.htaccess
        create app/puma.rb
